data.description: Charm Abounds! Lush Parklike Surroundings! Matadequin Creek views! Beautiful  home situated on 10 acres of tranquility near Pamunkey River. 1st floor boasts spacious eat-in kitchen w/custom cabinets, beamed ceiling & new appliances that flows into large family room w/brick fireplace. Family room opens to a bright sunroom w/deck access, featuring amazing backyard & Matadequin Creek views. Formal dining room, a sizable bedroom & full bath on the first floor, all w/hardwood floors, beautiful solid wood doors & central vac system. Upstairs features primary bedroom w/spacious walk-in closet & beautiful bath, along w/3 additional large bedrooms & full bath. Basement w/finished office/study, cozy rec room w/wood stove & convenient storage rm/workshop. BIG TICKET UPGRADES including new heat pumps, vinyl siding, replacement windows & newer dimensional roof & more! Storage shed/playhouse! Large unattached garage has the potential for a rental or short-term rental! AMAZING views of the natural surroundings from every window in house. Garage is to the right of the house up the hill a bit. Old Church area & great schools. Close to community center w/pool. Come & see! Some pics virtually staged.
